snippet: Red Sox fans usually come out in droves when their team is in Baltimore, but with the Orioles playing well, that has changed.
abstract: Boston Red Sox fans used to come in droves to away games at Camden Yards when their team would regularly beat the Baltimore Orioles, but most are staying away now that the teams' roles are reversed.
lead_paragraph: Red Sox fans usually come out in droves when their team is in Baltimore, but with the Orioles playing well, that has changed.

headline.seo: Buzz at Camden Yards Is for the Orioles Again
headline.main: At Camden Yards, Home Team Is Again a Draw for Fans
headline.print_headline: At Camden Yards, Home Team Is Again A Draw for Fans
